    dc:creator "Polhemus, Dan A." ;
    dc:date "2024" ;
    dc:title "Thirty-four new species of Rhagovelia (Heteroptera: Veliidae) from the East Papua Composite Terrane, far eastern New Guinea" ;
    bibo:endPage "214" ;
    bibo:issue "1" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2024-01-17" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "5400" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10659717>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10659779>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10659795>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10659797>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10659808> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10659717>
    dc:description "FIGS. 10, 11. Rhagovelia auga n. sp., wings; specimen from Mas River near Fane, Owen Stanley Mountains, New Guinea, CL 7257. 10. Forewing, showing the presence of two large distal closed cells of subequal length. 11. Hind wing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10659717/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10659779>
    dc:description "FIGS. 110–115. Rhagovelia dibuwa n. sp., structural details; specimens from Normanby Island. 110. Male right hind leg, weakly developed individual, posterior view. 111. Male right hind leg, weakly developed individual, dorsal view. 112. Male right hind leg, strongly developed individual, posterior view. 113. Male right hind leg, strongly developed individual, dorsal view; 110–113 from Dibuwa River, CL 7230. 114. Male left paramere, outer lateral view. 115 Male proctiger, dorsal view; 114 and 115 from Bunama, Apatabuia River, CL 7228." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10659779/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10659795>
    dc:description "FIGS. 133–138. Rhagovelia auga n. sp., structural details; specimens from New Guinea, Owen Stanley Range. 133. Wingless male, dorsal habitus; specimen from Udabe River, CL 7247. 134. Wingless female, dorsal habitus; specimen from Hane River, CL 7253. 135. Male right hind leg, posterior view. 136. Male right hind leg, dorsal view; 135 and 136 from Mas River, CL 7257. 137. Male left paramere, outer lateral view. 138. Male proctiger, dorsal view; 137 and 138 from Udabe River, CL 7247." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10659795/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10659797>
    dc:description "FIG. 139. Tributary to the upper Udabe River, near Woitape, Central Province, Papua New Guinea, CL 7247, habitat for R. auga n. sp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10659797/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10659808>
    dc:description "FIG. 153. Distributions of species in the R. auga and R. peggiae subgroups in eastern New Guinea." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10659808/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

